{"tid":1176603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<搞邊科>中國政府：批准台資銀行在大陸發行信用卡","createTime":"2019-05-29T10:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T15:53:25.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"725e96160cd608cf8b628bee741b2a7021905ee4","tid":1176603,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:23:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190529003151-260410?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20190529003151-260410%3Fchdtv&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1Lr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=922f1f48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190529003151-260410?chdtv</a><br />\n<br />\n新華社報導，大陸國台辦發言人安峰山29日在例行記者會上表示，富邦華一銀行獲批籌建信用卡業務，成為大陸首家獲批該業務的台資銀行，將為大陸的台胞台企享受更多金融服務提供更有力的支援。<br />\n會上，安峰山還介紹大陸各地各部門持續落實「31條惠及台胞措施」取得的新成效，包括上述金融合作方面成果。<br />\n安峰山表示，近1個月來，山東省陸續有濟南、煙台、泰安、棗莊、聊城、濟寧市等多個地方密集推出「31條措施」的具體實施意見，讓「31條措施」在山東省落實。<br />\n(工商 )"},{"pid":"c6fecabccb05f3ec2c43a04d9a2edbb7f28b1bb3","tid":1176603,"uid":44171,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"欠債唔還<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e703066c58283c80d0e497ae8d0a7395c695483a","tid":1176603,"uid":144372,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"c6fecabccb05f3ec2c43a04d9a2edbb7f28b1bb3","tid":1176603,"uid":44171,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"欠債唔還<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"大陸收入證明要開幾多都得<br />\n地址求其搵人寫都唔知真定假"},{"pid":"e755078a5cbe61651a685125ab31759584f89a5e","tid":1176603,"uid":13303,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:27:03.000Z","msg":"壞賬拖死台灣銀行支那又贏"},{"pid":"937eba2c7610066b57d6c83433a0f626ee1742b0","tid":1176603,"uid":25468,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyT